Titolo: Pokémon Home

Anno: 2020

Descrizione: Pokémon Home, stylized Pokémon HOME, is  free to download application for iOS and Android devices, and the Nintendo Switch system. The application was developed by ILCA and published by The Pokémon Company, and was released in February 2020. A successor to the Nintendo 3DS's Pokémon Bank service, Pokémon Home's main use is providing cloud-based storage for Pokémon, while also serving as a replacement for the 'Global Trade System' (GTS), and providing one-way-transfer of Pokémon from Pokémon Bank and Pokémon Go.
Currently, Pokémon Home is able to connect with Pokémon Go, Pokémon: Let's Go, Pikachu! and Let's Go, Eevee!, and Pokémon Sword and Shield. An update planned for sometime in 2022 will add support for Pokémon Brilliant Diamond and Shining Pearl and Pokémon Legends: Arceus.



